{"tid":2402743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佩洛西自違禁令繞過眾議院安檢 還拒繳罰款","createTime":"2021-02-10T15:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T15:28:59.000Z","uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"efe4c33119f73786765441873936ee7818bd5901","tid":2402743,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院民主黨籍議長裴洛西（Nancy Pelosi）在1月6日國會動亂事件之後，提議眾院入口處急設金屬探測門，避免議員攜帶武器入場，民主黨挾眾議院多數表決通過這項內規，並訂立罰責，不過裴洛西隨後卻被抓包帶頭違規，繞過安檢進入眾院，共和黨人敦促她繳交罰款遭拒絕！<br />\n<br />\n2月4日，2名共和黨議員因此被各罰5000美元（約台幣14萬3549元），眾議院共和黨議員要求警衛官對裴洛西進行罰款，因為她在進入國會時涉嫌繞過金屬探測器，違反了自己訂下的規定。<br />\n<br />\n該內規由裴洛西自己提議，眾院先前以216票對210票通過上述新規定。在1月6日動亂之後，國會山莊每個入口處，都在地板上安裝金屬探測器，並對特意繞過者開罰。初犯者罰款5000美元，其後每犯規一次，將罰1萬元（約台幣28萬7099元）。若議員在90天內不付款，將從薪水中扣除。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">裴洛西當時曾表示，任何繞過新安全措施者，「都是拒絕遵守基本預防措施，不尊重維護安全的英雄。」她還批評許多眾院共和黨人對國會警察「不敬」，口出惡言，並拒絕遵守基本的預防性措施，以確保議員和警察等國會成員安全。</span><br />\n<br />\n沒想到裴洛西似乎嚴以待人，自己卻不守規定。<span class=\"red\">多名共和黨眾議員，在一封寫給眾議院警衛官的信中說，2月5日上午9點59分左右，「多名成員目睹眾議院議長在沒有完成安檢的情況下，進入眾院會議廳。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">儘管共和黨人敦促裴洛西繳罰款，但她迄今裝聾作啞，不予理會。</span>針對裴洛西的違規，國會警衛官布洛傑特（Timothy Blodgett）在給《國會山莊報》（The Hill）的聲明中表示，他還沒有收到國會警察對此事件的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3436953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3436953&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=e9bdd114\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3436953&h=a4b64c31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3436953</a>"},{"pid":"339fbc0f29dd8985de081bef20c1962878b3d662","tid":2402743,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca953cb551ecd57bf1c82bd922bfc7d88fcda4d","tid":2402743,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/09/185251_a787086dd66ee88cc9b3611ea2a9813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2F185251_a787086dd66ee88cc9b3611ea2a9813a.jpg&h=3d695f81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dc0ba98f345065bcf81dc625c260a560c86e0af","tid":2402743,"uid":256837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:22:09.000Z","msg":"西婆有特權㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9556daa1d9740b20b1e794eaeca0dadc74af77e1","tid":2402743,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"Rules for thee but not for me<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534a9199f8430fde048d8851e03b949b47e350ca","tid":2402743,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307518bc7e19522882055630e6857d0e72a7712a","tid":2402743,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"佩洛閪"}]}